This plugin for Puppet adds a resource type and provider for managing Glassfish
domains by using the asadmin command line tool.

Example:

glassfish {
    "mydomain":
        portbase => "4800",
        adminuser => "admin",
        passwordfile => "/home/gfish/.aspass",
        profile => "cluster",
        ensure => present;

    "myolddomain":
        ensure => absent;
}
